Dialogue: 0,0:01:37.63,0:01:40.45,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真是的 总是说超啊超的…
Dialogue: 0,0:01:40.45,0:01:43.06,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,都快成达兹纳大叔的口头禅了
Dialogue: 0,0:01:43.06,0:01:44.66,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,说什么呢
Dialogue: 0,0:01:44.66,0:01:48.69,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你看起来变得超可靠啊
Dialogue: 0,0:01:50.23,0:01:51.71,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,果然看起来很可靠吧
Dialogue: 0,0:01:51.88,0:01:53.50,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,超可靠呢
Dialogue: 0,0:01:55.59,0:01:57.62,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你对拍马屁还真是没辙啊
Dialogue: 0,0:01:57.62,0:01:58.96,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你这不害臊的家伙
Dialogue: 0,0:01:59.96,0:02:02.21,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我可是超认真的哦
Dialogue: 0,0:02:02.36,0:02:03.26,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是真的
Dialogue: 0,0:02:03.26,0:02:06.57,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,鸣人哥哥在我们国家可是英雄啊
Dialogue: 0,0:02:07.08,0:02:09.34,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,据说如此哦 小樱
Dialogue: 0,0:02:11.82,0:02:14.02,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,现在或许是吧
Dialogue: 0,0:02:14.13,0:02:15.56,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,什么
Dialogue: 0,0:02:15.99,0:02:20.51,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,过去总是自以为是 到处惹事啊
Dialogue: 0,0:02:21.38,0:02:24.79,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,第七班那时真的很开心啊
Dialogue: 0,0:02:26.54,0:02:27.83,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:02:30.07,0:02:31.43,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,很开心
Dialogue: 0,0:02:32.17,0:02:34.39,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,还记得吗 那位大叔
Dialogue: 0,0:02:34.39,0:02:35.52,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,要复仇的那个
Dialogue: 0,0:02:36.36,0:02:39.39,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,兹卡德大叔 真让人怀念啊
Dialogue: 0,0:02:39.70,0:02:41.42,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那时你也是的
Dialogue: 0,0:02:41.60,0:02:44.25,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,自作主张 惹出不少事来啊
Dialogue: 0,0:02:50.80,0:02:53.63,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,既然在此碰见 就说明你的末日到了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:54.23,0:02:56.15,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我族的不共戴天之敌
Dialogue: 0,0:02:56.27,0:03:00.24,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,卡塔兹 痛快地一决胜负吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:06.29,0:03:07.71,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,无论怎么看
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.71,0:03:11.17,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这家伙都想把我生吞活剥啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.36,0:03:12.75,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎么会呢
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.83,0:03:14.47,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,长得相当可爱不是吗
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.70,0:03:17.81,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,总之 谁让你猜拳输了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.81,0:03:19.96,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,照顾鸵鸟一职就非你莫属了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.66,0:03:23.08,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没事 没事
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.31,0:03:25.37,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你们俩意外地般配呢
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.80,0:03:30.07,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,到底哪里般配了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.07,0:03:33.37,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,痛 痛 好痛…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.82,0:03:37.52,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,从走失的猫到走失的狗 再到走失的猪…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.68,0:03:39.54,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,终于轮到走失的鸵鸟了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.20,0:03:41.94,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,体型变大倒是不错
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.31,0:03:44.40,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但尽是这些无聊的任务
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.62,0:03:46.19,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,能力根本无法提升啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.74,0:03:51.35,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,所谓任务 并不是用来提升忍者的技能
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.81,0:03:54.21,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这和修行可不同
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.14,0:04:01.67,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我能理解你急切的心情
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.16,0:04:07.37,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那就用鸵鸟做对手 来提升你的能力吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.37,0:04:09.23,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你想干吗
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.23,0:04:11.79,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,管他呢 快点开始吧 你不是要…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.89,0:04:15.79,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好疼…住手啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.87,0:04:24.06,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就在这里找家旅馆休息吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.48,0:04:26.97,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,鸵鸟先生也该累了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.31,0:04:28.56,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真是的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.86,0:04:30.53,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,如果只有我们的话
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.62,0:04:33.35,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在日落之前就能回村了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.60,0:04:40.13,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那边怎么了 我去看看
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.13,0:04:42.27,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,鸣人 你又…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.33,0:04:45.38,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,去看看吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.51,0:04:46.69,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎么回事
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.78,0:04:48.30,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎么连你们也…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.47,0:04:53.37,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,打架吗
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.37,0:04:55.51,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不…像是在复仇
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.01,0:04:57.47,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,复仇
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.69,0:05:01.58,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,复仇…有人要报仇雪恨吗
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.10,0:05:04.41,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,仇恨…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.20,0:05:09.10,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,光天化日之下 聚众血拼没问题吗 卡卡西老师
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.80,0:05:13.17,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,复仇许可书
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.73,0:05:14.86,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,根据某些国家规定
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.86,0:05:16.44,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,当某人被杀害后
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.59,0:05:20.15,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,许可其遗族进行复仇
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.63,0:05:23.35,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,如果持有该国所发的许可证书
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.40,0:05:26.20,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,即使在其他国家也能进行复仇行动
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.72,0:05:31.04,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好像是那位兹卡德大叔的远房亲戚
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.13,0:05:34.07,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,半夜被那个仇家叫了出去
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.48,0:05:38.33,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,太过分了 在背后用大石头暗算
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.41,0:05:40.57,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,被残忍地杀害了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.74,0:05:43.15,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,为了追杀仇人
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.24,0:05:45.75,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那位大叔被族人推选了出来
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.47,0:05:49.76,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真是个大坏蛋啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.15,0:05:51.61,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,金蚊老大
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.66,0:05:53.49,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好像有人在复仇呢
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.26,0:05:56.91,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,看起来蛮有趣的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.95,0:05:59.61,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你们觉得哪方会赢
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.61,0:06:03.83,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,俗话说得好…狼总比兔子跑得快啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.43,0:06:10.89,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,未必哦 仇敌一方似乎胸有成竹 面不改色呢
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.32,0:06:25.48,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,出手了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.48,0:06:26.45,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不要啊…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.87,0:06:37.36,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这下可报不了仇了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.91,0:06:44.64,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,什么…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.61,0:06:50.25,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,给我等等
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.66,0:06:52.24,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你这混账…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.86,0:06:58.47,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,混蛋…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.47,0:06:59.48,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,给你
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.62,0:07:01.84,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不好意思
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.06,0:07:05.35,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就差那么一点点
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.40,0:07:07.88,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,完全没看出来
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.71,0:07:11.14,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,门外汉给我闭嘴
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.33,0:07:12.65,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,别小瞧我
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.65,0:07:15.21,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好歹我也是有过34回复仇经验的专家
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.01,0:07:20.71,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那岂不是失败34回了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.81,0:07:21.95,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,下次一定成功…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.95,0:07:23.55,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不现实…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.92,0:07:28.23,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,无论如何 我都要复仇
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.85,0:07:31.47,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一定要替族人鹿藏大叔报仇雪恨
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.07,0:07:35.05,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,从背后偷袭的卑鄙行为
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.76,0:07:37.60,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,如果此仇无法昭雪的话…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.12,0:07:40.61,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我…我…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.88,0:07:42.16,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,大叔
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.62,0:07:46.27,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你的话对我太过残忍了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.20,0:07:49.72,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不试试又怎么能知道呢
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.98,0:07:54.59,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,下次或许就能成功复仇了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.00,0:07:59.68,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我明白了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.14,0:08:03.48,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我来助你一臂之力吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.71,0:08:06.85,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我会运用全部的忍者技能
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.93,0:08:09.59,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,来帮大叔成为一代复仇宗师
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.38,0:08:14.75,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,笨蛋鸣人
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.77,0:08:15.99,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,又在逞能了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.80,0:08:18.58,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这里就暂时交给鸣人吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.64,0:08:21.25,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们先回旅馆休息吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.75,0:08:22.91,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真是无聊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.95,0:08:26.47,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,大叔 安心交给我吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.23,0:08:32.59,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,第一课
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.41,0:08:36.74,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,大叔的复仇愤怒指标不够
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.92,0:08:40.64,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,应当无论何时都能瞬间爆发出怒火
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.20,0:08:43.76,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这样面对突如其来的复仇 就不会手忙脚乱了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.59,0:08:49.23,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你这混蛋
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.57,0:08:51.63,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,老太婆 很危险啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.76,0:08:53.74,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就让我来背你这混蛋吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.47,0:08:56.04,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你这混蛋要去哪儿呢
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.04,0:08:57.83,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就去那旁边的小路
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.94,0:08:59.42,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,很近啊 混蛋
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.09,0:09:01.98,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,再远点也没关系啊 混蛋
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.44,0:09:03.45,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎么觉得有点…不对
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.26,0:09:06.73,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,第二课
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.25,0:09:10.06,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,即便是丁点的仇恨 也不能轻易放过
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.09,0:09:11.48,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,让复仇融入生活吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.09,0:09:16.36,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我说…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.97,0:09:18.23,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我来帮你报仇
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.04,0:09:26.92,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,撞肩之恨 撞肩之仇 撞肩之怨…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.39,0:09:23.79,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,给我住手啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.03,0:09:26.23,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,果然还是不对
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.56,0:09:27.57,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好痛啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.57,0:09:30.13,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,第三课
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.40,0:09:33.08,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,心中要充满了对敌人的怨恨
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.08,0:09:35.46,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,从而将那股怨恨淋漓尽致地发泄于手
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.04,0:09:46.65,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,什么啊 被憎恨的仇家怎么会如此清秀
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.67,0:09:54.10,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,大叔果然不适合当复仇者啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.54,0:09:57.06,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你也不适合当教官
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.26,0:10:01.34,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,为何如此执着于复仇呢
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.56,0:10:05.20,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不然我无脸返回家乡啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.63,0:10:08.58,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真想尽快了结此事 然后回家
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.47,0:10:12.13,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,回到年迈的父母的身边
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.21,0:10:17.01,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,鸵鸟发疯了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.00,0:10:31.23,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,大叔
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.63,0:10:33.08,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那家伙…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.18,0:10:34.97,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,隐藏身手啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.97,0:10:35.70,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你们还呆着干吗
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.60,0:10:42.52,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不好意思
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.64,0:10:44.63,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,鸵鸟咬断了绳子
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.84,0:10:49.96,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你果然身手不凡啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.84,0:10:53.68,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,到底是怎么回事
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.86,0:10:55.66,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,大叔明明那么厉害
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.75,0:10:58.03,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,为什么始终不能复仇呢
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.83,0:11:00.95,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不知道
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.17,0:11:03.45,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,每当看到那家伙的眼神
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.97,0:11:05.83,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,力量就逐渐消失了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.98,0:11:11.66,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那眼神…那眼神
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.95,0:11:15.21,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,大叔
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.73,0:11:24.52,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,大叔在那之后怎样了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.09,0:11:28.54,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,估计为了复仇 再度启程了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.96,0:11:31.67,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,会永远持续下去吗
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.98,0:11:35.99,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那是…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.33,0:11:39.78,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,如何 想报仇的老兄
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.84,0:11:42.64,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们被你的真诚所打动
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.72,0:11:45.13,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,为了让你完成复仇
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.13,0:11:47.19,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们把这家伙带回来了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.49,0:11:50.35,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就请毫无顾忌地来场复仇之战吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.71,0:11:54.87,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,大叔
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.89,0:11:55.92,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,对了…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:55.92,0:12:00.18,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这场决斗要让我们金蚊一家来组织
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.48,0:12:02.26,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好了 诸位
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.50,0:12:04.44,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这场决斗到底谁是最后的赢家呢
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.55,0:12:06.81,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好了 下注吧 下注吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.82,0:12:09.10,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,到底哪一边比较强呢
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.11,0:12:10.48,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,肯定是仇家更厉害啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.48,0:12:13.74,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那大叔太无能了 毫无胜算
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.74,0:12:15.41,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那我赌仇家500两
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.41,0:12:16.45,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我也是
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.35,0:12:21.93,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那赌金少的一方就算我金蚊的
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.62,0:12:24.96,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,如果那大叔使出真本领的话
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.96,0:12:26.52,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,胜负就…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.46,0:12:29.64,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,能让我大赚一把了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.83,0:12:31.36,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真可恶
Dialogue: 0,0:12:31.53,0:12:34.34,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,竟然利用大叔的复仇来赚钱
Dialogue: 0,0:12:37.86,0:12:39.51,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一切到此为此吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:40.00,0:12:42.97,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,同意 我不会轻易被你杀掉的
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.76,0:12:47.74,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,来吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.41,0:12:57.77,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,难道说 不看对方的眼睛
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.81,0:13:08.61,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这样或许会赢
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.65,0:13:11.40,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,难道说鸣人的指导奏效了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.26,0:13:20.30,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,总觉得…总觉得这场决斗让人很不舒服
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.93,0:13:22.07,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,到底为什么…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.04,0:13:26.09,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是那家伙…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.41,0:13:27.99,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,正像大叔所说的那样
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.25,0:13:30.62,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那家伙的脸…眼神…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.39,0:13:41.79,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那眼神
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.92,0:13:43.84,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,为什么要流露出那样的眼神
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.22,0:13:46.82,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,明明可能被我杀掉啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.99,0:13:53.12,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,为什么不打算伤害大叔…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.15,0:14:00.42,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,既然如此…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.60,0:14:09.32,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,给我等等
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.12,0:14:14.69,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,无论如何都无法对他下手的理由
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.02,0:14:18.96,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,大叔现在应该心知肚明了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:24.32,0:14:26.13,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,弄明白了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.06,0:14:29.71,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,原来如此 刀刃是钝的
Dialogue: 0,0:14:30.29,0:14:33.20,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这家伙是不会杀人的
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.65,0:14:41.04,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我有个双胞胎弟弟 名叫影木
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.74,0:14:44.03,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,双胞胎弟弟…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:44.43,0:14:49.34,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,影木曾借钱给你族的鹿藏
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.63,0:14:52.61,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但因生了孩子急需用钱
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.65,0:14:54.91,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,便前去催促还钱
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.40,0:14:59.34,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,而鹿藏却装傻 矢口否认借钱一事
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.85,0:15:04.73,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,结果两人起了争执 一起倒地
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.97,0:15:10.11,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,然而鹿藏倒地时 碰到了晒干货的石头
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.93,0:15:12.03,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,然后就…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.72,0:15:15.14,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你想说这是意外事故吗
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.34,0:15:17.61,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,影木打算去自首
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.21,0:15:20.22,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是没有目击者
Dialogue: 0,0:15:20.89,0:15:24.58,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,从证据来看 他毫无疑问是个杀人犯
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.67,0:15:26.73,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,所以我决定代替他
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.46,0:15:28.79,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,什么…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.31,0:15:31.39,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我成为了弟弟
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.46,0:15:36.08,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,而弟弟则同他的妻子以及刚出生的孩子隐姓埋名
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.27,0:15:42.09,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,而我则故意暴露身份 吸引追杀者
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.96,0:15:45.87,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,绝不能让那样的好人糟蹋了人生
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.19,0:15:51.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我是个恶人 给社会 家人 朋友添尽了麻烦
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.70,0:15:54.08,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,以此来赎罪 再合适不过了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:54.72,0:15:56.51,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我是这么认为的
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.54,0:15:59.72,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,所有的一切都是我弟弟的片面之词
Dialogue: 0,0:16:00.23,0:16:02.31,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没有真凭实据
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.74,0:16:05.29,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不过我相信他
Dialogue: 0,0:16:07.08,0:16:08.15,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,大叔
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.29,0:16:13.18,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,信不信由你
Dialogue: 0,0:16:13.59,0:16:17.70,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不相信的话 就杀了我吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.30,0:16:24.37,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就姑且信你一回吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.37,0:16:25.90,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你… 大叔
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.33,0:16:29.66,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我对复仇有些厌倦了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.08,0:16:33.41,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一直以来 你都装作有罪
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.81,0:16:36.99,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这次就由我来装作复仇好了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.57,0:16:44.37,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那可不行
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.66,0:16:48.49,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,无论如何 你都要报仇
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.31,0:16:54.11,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不然 你们可就惨了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.43,0:16:56.75,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我也来帮忙吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:57.17,0:16:58.35,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们也…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.44,0:16:59.45,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,…来拔刀相助
Dialogue: 0,0:17:00.91,0:17:02.13,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真是没辙
Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.57,0:17:05.59,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,谁让我想要早些回村子里修行呢
Dialogue: 0,0:17:05.88,0:17:07.75,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我也来参合一下
Dialogue: 0,0:17:14.13,0:17:15.62,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,给我上
Dialogue: 0,0:17:29.13,0:17:31.26,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你们给我记着
Dialogue: 0,0:17:41.56,0:17:44.62,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这样就行了吧 卡卡西老师
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.94,0:17:47.81,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那是他俩决定的
Dialogue: 0,0:17:48.65,0:17:51.84,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,复仇还真是辛苦啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:52.83,0:17:54.91,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你怎么可能明白呢
Dialogue: 0,0:17:55.94,0:17:57.10,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,即便如此
Dialogue: 0,0:17:57.11,0:17:59.52,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,也有不得不报之仇
Dialogue: 0,0:18:08.62,0:18:10.43,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那时候的我们…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:10.50,0:18:13.56,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不 是我还太幼稚
Dialogue: 0,0:18:13.81,0:18:14.86,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,佐助
Dialogue: 0,0:18:17.46,0:18:19.25,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你们已经到了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:19.36,0:18:20.60,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,卡卡西先生
Dialogue: 0,0:18:20.88,0:18:22.48,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是卡卡西啊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:22.54,0:18:24.39,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,因为木叶发生了大事嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:18:24.39,0:18:26.24,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,当然要马上赶来啊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:27.04,0:18:28.53,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,原来如此啊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:31.05,0:18:32.10,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎么了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:32.43,0:18:34.07,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,佐助呢
Dialogue: 0,0:18:34.07,0:18:36.49,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我还想跟他聊聊呢
Dialogue: 0,0:18:42.38,0:18:43.77,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,事…事实上…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:44.04,0:18:46.18,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,佐助他…这个…那个…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:47.00,0:18:50.60,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,佐助呢 因为跟我吵架
Dialogue: 0,0:18:50.70,0:18:52.74,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,所以离开了村子
Dialogue: 0,0:18:52.91,0:18:55.47,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没事 很快就会把他给带回来的
Dialogue: 0,0:18:55.75,0:18:58.03,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,等他回来后再跟他打招呼吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:58.19,0:19:00.64,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,到时佐助也会很高兴的
Dialogue: 0,0:19:00.75,0:19:02.29,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,对吧 小樱
Dialogue: 0,0:19:04.48,0:19:07.78,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,什么嘛 因为三角关系闹出纠纷了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:19:07.84,0:19:12.06,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真讨厌 才没有那回事呢
Dialogue: 0,0:19:12.22,0:19:14.08,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,谢谢你 鸣人
Dialogue: 0,0:19:19.49,0:19:20.64,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,佐助
Dialogue: 0,0:19:20.93,0:19:22.71,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你现在到底在哪里啊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:29.45,0:19:31.67,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没有父母兄弟的你
Dialogue: 0,0:19:31.79,0:19:33.78,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎么可能理解我
Dialogue: 0,0:19:34.27,0:19:36.49,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,从一开始就孤身一人的你
Dialogue: 0,0:19:36.57,0:19:38.57,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎么可能理解我啊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:39.99,0:19:42.04,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,正是因为有羁绊才会感到痛苦
Dialogue: 0,0:19:42.53,0:19:44.68,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一旦失去羁绊又将如何
Dialogue: 0,0:19:45.03,0:19:46.53,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,像你这种家伙…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:51.24,0:19:52.63,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我现在能够了解了…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:53.44,0:19:55.07,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,佐助的心情
Dialogue: 0,0:19:57.61,0:20:00.71,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,所谓复仇到底是什么
Dialogue: 0,0:20:04.36,0:20:07.22,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,能理解一些痛楚了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:20:07.71,0:20:09.92,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,如果没有承受过相同的痛楚
Dialogue: 0,0:20:10.04,0:20:12.65,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就无法真正的理解他人
Dialogue: 0,0:20:14.40,0:20:17.63,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我曾以为自己很了解佐助
Dialogue: 0,0:20:18.29,0:20:20.71,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可实际上我根本不了解
Dialogue: 0,0:20:21.40,0:20:25.24,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,所以 无论我在终结之谷对佐助说什么
Dialogue: 0,0:20:25.42,0:20:27.16,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他都无动于衷
Dialogue: 0,0:20:27.37,0:20:28.46,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,鸣人
Dialogue: 0,0:20:28.57,0:20:30.51,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不了解佐助的痛苦
Dialogue: 0,0:20:30.62,0:20:32.53,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是不可能跟他一同欢笑的
Dialogue: 0,0:20:32.91,0:20:36.23,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就连跟他打架的资格都没有
Dialogue: 0,0:20:38.88,0:20:41.38,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,或许会很痛
Dialogue: 0,0:20:41.56,0:20:44.38,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但之后我想跟他好好地打一架啊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:44.58,0:20:46.74,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,总有一天会让佐助回来的
Dialogue: 0,0:20:46.86,0:20:50.14,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,第七班的所有人也能一起欢笑了
Dialogue: 0,0:22:36.79,0:22:39.11,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,汇合地点的确就是这里
Dialogue: 0,0:22:39.16,0:22:41.24,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,看来是我们先到了
Dialogue: 0,0:22:41.24,0:22:42.33,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真是的
Dialogue: 0,0:22:42.38,0:22:44.82,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,难得的协作任务竟然迟到…
Dialogue: 0,0:22:44.99,0:22:48.60,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,砂隐真的有意向木叶修好吗
Dialogue: 0,0:22:48.60,0:22:50.24,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,迟到了 真抱歉
Dialogue: 0,0:22:50.75,0:22:52.13,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你是…
Dialogue: 0,0:22:52.14,0:22:53.28,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎么偏偏是…
Dialogue: 0,0:22:53.32,0:22:55.52,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没想到和这家伙合作
Dialogue: 0,0:22:55.81,0:22:57.66,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,下集 火影忍者疾风传
Dialogue: 0,0:22:57.76,0:22:59.54,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我爱罗 羁绊
Dialogue: 0,0:23:00.51,0:23:03.26,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,同盟国的伙伴们 大家要好好相处啊
